      <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Every licensed healthcare provider who bills Medicare or Medicaid has a unique NPI number in the CMS NPPES registry. Start there to verify a provider's name, specialty, and practice location before your first visit. Then check state licensure and board certification to complete the picture.</p>
